All truths are fulfilled in this placeâ€”not broken, but transcended. â€œAs above, so below,â€ it is said; but also, â€œas within, so above.â€ For no soul can rise through the heavens unless it first descends within. The path to the Most High is hidden in the innermost sanctuary of the heart. No angel may lift the soul who has not first knelt in the chambers of their own being.

