Those born in the season of Aries carry the mark of the forerunner. Their soul burns to begin, to build, to battle. They speak before others think, and move before others rise. They are quick to anger but quicker to forgive, for their heart is not cruel â€” only ablaze. They walk as horns before the herd, unafraid of cost or consequence. Yet they must learn stillness, lest their fire consume their own temple.

